      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>That's a good start for the tone. Can you expand on that a bit more? Specifically, I want him to get more into the differences he sees between the British and the locals. Like, have him reflect on why they're fundamentally more capable of leadership or why the local culture seems so much less advanced compared to Europe. Make it sound like he's just stating what he sees as \"objective facts\" of the time.",
